item.title: [HBASE-4957] Clean up some log messages, code in RecoverableZooKeeper
item.description: In RecoverableZooKeeper, there are a number of log messages and comments which don't really read correctly, and some other pieces of code that can be cleaned up. Simple cleanup - shouldn't be any actual behavioral changes.
item.summary: Clean up some log messages, code in RecoverableZooKeeper

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.
